# Inventory Report (CANON)

## Before editing

1. `Reports/Inventory/AGENTS.md`
2. `Reports/Inventory/Module/Project Memory/DECISIONS.md` (naming, stock cover, landed cost)
3. `Reports/Inventory/Module/Project Memory/REFERENCE.md` (page IDs)

## Fabric vs module

- **Fabric review:** edit `Fabric/DevelopmentWorkspace/Canon Inventory Report.pbip`
- **Module home:** `Reports/Inventory/Companies/CANON/Canon Inventory Report/`
- Mirror display-label / report-definition changes to both unless user scopes to one copy.

## Do not undo (user-approved)

- Page tabs: Inventory Overview, Stock Value, Stock Health, Stock Actions, Landed Cost
- Labels: **Overstock Value**, **Open PO**, **Open SO**, **Stock Status**, **LC Doc**
- Landed Cost: **Import & Handling Costs** is not **Total Landed Cost**

## Archive

Completed prompts/handoffs live in `Reports/Inventory/Module/Archive/` — not active `Project Memory/`.

Codex skill: `powerbi-inventory-report` (`~/.codex/skills/`).
